sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Administrator
    participant App as Kiosk App (Virtual or Physical)
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant VB as Vision Box (Kiosk A)

    Note over Admin,App: Admin logs in via the app
    Admin->>App: Logs in and opens Admin Dashboard
    App->>API: GET /api/v1/kiosks [With JWT Admin Token]
    API-->>App: 200 OK (List of kiosks)

    alt 1. Locker Grid UI
        Admin->>App: Selects Kiosk A and opens Locker Grid
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/kiosks/{kiosk_id}/lockers
        API->>DB: Fetch physical status of lockers
        DB-->>API: Statuses (e.g. AVAILABLE, MAINTENANCE, OCCUPIED)
        API-->>App: 200 OK (Current status per locker)

        opt Force Door Open
            Admin->>App: Taps Locker 1 -> Force Open
            App->>API: POST /api/v1/lockers/{locker_id}/open
            Note over API: Validates Admin role
            API->>VB: WSS: open_slot {locker_id: {locker_id}}
            VB-->>API: WSS: slot_opened
            API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs {action_type: 'ADMIN_FORCED_OPEN'}
            API-->>App: 200 OK (Locker opened)
        end

        opt Mark as Defective
            Admin->>App: Taps Locker 1 -> Mark MAINTENANCE
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/lockers/{locker_id}/status {locker_status: 'MAINTENANCE'}
            API->>DB: UPDATE lockers SET locker_status = 'MAINTENANCE' WHERE locker_id = {locker_id}
            API-->>App: 200 OK (Locker marked)
        end

    else 2. Quarantine Inbox
        Admin->>App: Opens Quarantine Inbox
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/loans?status=PENDING_INSPECTION
        API-->>App: List of loans in quarantine
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/evaluations/{evaluation_id}
        API-->>App: Photo, AI report, damage details
        Note right of App: See [sequence_quarantine.mmd](./sequence_quarantine.mmd) for handling

    else 3. Asset Catalog
        Admin->>App: Opens Asset Management
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/assets [With JWT Admin Token]
        API->>DB: SELECT a.*, l.loan_status, u.first_name, u.last_name FROM assets a LEFT JOIN loans l ON a.asset_id = l.asset_id AND l.loan_status IN ('ACTIVE', 'RESERVED') LEFT JOIN users u ON l.user_id = u.user_id WHERE a.is_deleted = FALSE
        DB-->>API: Full list (Asset + Locker info + Borrower)
        API-->>App: 200 OK (Admin view)
        
        opt New Asset
            Admin->>App: Adds asset
            App->>API: POST /api/v1/assets
            API->>DB: INSERT INTO assets
            API-->>App: 201 Created
        end
        
        opt Delete Asset (Soft Delete)
            Admin->>App: Deletes asset
            App->>API: DELETE /api/v1/assets/{asset_id}
            Note over API,DB: Soft-deletes the specific asset (catalog/checkout filter is_deleted = FALSE)
            API->>DB: UPDATE assets SET is_deleted = TRUE WHERE asset_id = {asset_id}
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end

    else 4. User & NFC Management
        Admin->>App: Opens User Management
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/users [With JWT Admin Token]
        API-->>App: List of users
        
        opt Unblock User
            Admin->>App: Unblocks account
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/users/{user_id} {failed_login_attempts: 0, locked_until: null}
            Note over API,DB: Reset failed attempts & lock timer
            API->>DB: UPDATE users SET failed_login_attempts = 0, locked_until = NULL WHERE user_id = {user_id}
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end
        
        opt Link NFC Tag
            Admin->>App: Links new NFC tag
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/users/{user_id}/nfc {nfc_tag_id}
            Note over API,DB: Update column in users table
            API->>DB: UPDATE users SET nfc_tag_id = {nfc_tag_id} WHERE user_id = {user_id}
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end
    end